org.oucs.gaboto.entities.pool
Class GabotoEntityPoolConfiguration

java.lang.Object
  org.oucs.gaboto.entities.pool.GabotoEntityPoolConfiguration

public class GabotoEntityPoolConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object

Used to configure the creation of GabotoEntityPools.

An GabotoEntityPool can either be created from an GabotoSnapshot or from a Jena Model and an Gaboto object. This can be seen as the source from which the pool is created. All other options define which entities from the source are to be added to the pool.

Version:
0.1
Author:
Arno Mittelbach
See Also:
GabotoEntityPool
